 and each one offers Technology That Listens. The Moshi Voice-Activated Reflection alarm clock is no exception, offering voice-activation technology to make it easy to set the alarm clock. Its small size makes it easy to take on vacation or use anywhere in your home.","Moshi is known for their innovative and creative consumer electronics, and their Reflection alarm clock fits that same criteria. For such a small device, the first thing you might notice is the extensive amount of buttons on the clock. These are very simple to navigate through, but the Moshi Voice-Recognition Technology means you can choose not to use the buttons to set up the clock. By activating the voice recognition switch, you can ask Moshi to set the time, the date and any alarms, and even snooze function can be voice-activated. Like all Moshi products, this is pre-programmed to recognize all your voice commands as soon as you pull it out of the box.","This alarm clock radio comes with six station presets to use with the AM/FM radio. There are three different alarm sounds and sleep sounds. A voice memo function is also featured on this clock. You can record voice memos up to eight minutes in length, a very useful feature if you tend to have a hectic schedule in the morning and need to remember something. Moshi is always looking out for you.","The clock display features six nighttime colors that you can switch between. The LCD screen has adjustable brightness, but the highest level seems to be too bright in a dark room. And as if there weren&#39;t enough features, there is an AUX-IN port on the back of the clock so you can plug your MP3 player into it, although you can&#39;t use the MP3 function as an alarm.","The clock also displays the indoor and outdoor temperatures, and even shows the outside humidity level. The outside temperature is relayed from an external wireless sensor. However, be aware that there is some trouble with the temperature readings, as the outside temperate can display up to 100 degrees warmer than it actually is. Chances are, you will be able to tell the difference, but it is an inconvenience for this function not to operate properly.","Moshi gets the design right when it comes to alarm clocks. Moshi made the Reflection alarm clock to fit any style. The clock measures only five inches wide and three inches deep so its conveniently transported from spot to spot, even for those who travel. The sleek and glossy finish gives the clock a futuristic look. Be wary, though, as the glass on the front of the clock is just that – glass.  The glass breaks easily when dropped and can get scratched if it comes in contact with certain objects. It does give this alarm clock a nice, attractive, reflective finish, but as with all glass products, treat it with caution.","If you run into any snags with the device, such as broken glass or defective temperature readings, the Moshi Reflection Clock comes with a one-year warranty.  The customer service page of Moshi&#39;s website hosts user manuals and FAQs, though there is not any information that is specific to the Reflection alarm clock. If necessary, you can contact Moshi by phone or through email."]},"id":"9fcb03d1-0284-40a9-a334-f784f1be73dc","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"5e7187d8-19cb-4c02-b1ee-1b7278011b5f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["If you&#39;re looking for an alarm clock that you can use both home and on the road, the Moshi Voice-Activated Reflection alarm clock does just that. Its size allows you to pack it in a travel bag, and it&#39;s the perfect size to fit any home environment. You may run into snags with the outdoor temperature readings, but the clock is covered by a one-year warranty."]},"id":"8bada0a8-6185-4301-9cdf-8080ac0ffc79","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_54011","url":"/moshi-voice-activated-reflection-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"billy-bommer","url":"/author/billy-bommer","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","nam